It makes its nest by damming
streams with bark and mud. It is
known as an industrious worker.

While its movements out of water
are sluggish, it can swim as fast
as any FEEBAS.

A river dammed by BIBAREL will
never overflow its banks, which
is appreciated by people nearby.

It busily makes its nest with
stacks of branches and roots it
has cut up with its sharp incisors.

Il tranche les branches et les racines de ses incisives
aiguises pour construire des barrages.

Emsig durchbeit es mit seinen scharfen Vorderzhnen
Wurzeln und ste und baut daraus sein Nest.

Con sus incisivos roe ramas y races y las apila para
construir sus madrigueras junto al ro.

Costruisce con zelo la tana in riva ai corsi dacqua,
levigando radici e rami con gli affilati incisivi.

Il construit des barrages de boue et dcorce le long
des fleuves. Cest un ouvrier de renom.

Es baut sein Nest, indem es in Flssen Dmme aus
Schlamm und sten baut. Ein fleiiger Arbeiter.

Para anidar, crea presas en los ros con maderas y
barro. Tiene fama de trabajador.

Sbarra il corso dei fiumi con corteccia e fango per
farsi la tana.  noto come lavoratore instancabile.
